Texts.Chs: 我发现邪教徒正在密谋腐化古老的仙灵之森，而我将阻止它们的恶行。另外为了完成任务，我得准备好抓钩，它是这项任务的必要装备，所以如果我还没有的话，那么我应该在出发前制作一个。
Texts.Eng: I've discovered a nefarious cultist plot to corrupt an ancient forest. It's up to me to stop them! I've been advised that a grappling hook will be necessary to complete this mission, so I should get one before I go.
